    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255190/extras/27f5396686ea76d7f73b55f25d6d6509.poster.avif?t=1766484746\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255190/extras/27f5396686ea76d7f73b55f25d6d6509.webm?t=1766484746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255190/extras/27f5396686ea76d7f73b55f25d6d6509.mp4?t=1766484746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>FUMES</strong></i> 是一款单人游戏，其灵感来自黄金时代的车辆战斗类型。游戏玩法直截了当、节奏明快、紧张刺激。坐进车内，带上武器，在扭曲的荒原上巡航。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有废话。只有你、你的车和纯粹的乐趣。就像过去一样！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >功能</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶可定制的汽车。给汽车配备武器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验受到老式拉力赛游戏启发的物理驾驶。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遭遇一波又一波的敌人。参与追逐破坏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定制你的汽车。选择适合自己战斗风格的装备。贴上一些贴纸。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过击败 <strong>Boss</strong> 获得新车和零件。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无加载屏幕。没有快速旅行。只需使用你的汽车。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗结束后减速，兜风并吸入 <i><strong>FUMES</strong></i>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在沙漠中迷失方向。在无尽的程序化环境中漫步。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >聆听原汁原味的吉他配乐。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255190/extras/f7e2cf37c12503a5ef9fa8cdea236b79.avif?t=1766484746\" width=616 height=577 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >漫游荒原，收集废料，燃烧你的方式通过挑战，成为混乱行者...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >......或者干脆加入我们的 <strong>Discord</strong> 服务器，与我们和其他像你一样的旅行者一起玩耍。参与创造这个扭曲的世界！</p>",
